    "(3.40)The first two lines of R.H.S. are the full index of N = 4 USp(2N) gauge theory and the last line is the contribution from the half-hyper living at the interface.",
    "JHEP12(2024)227In fact, we find that the half-indices (3.39) and (3.40) beautifully agree with each other!",
