    "(3.41)More generally, when N D3-branes in x 6 < 0 end on a half NS5-brane from one side and M D3-branes in x 6 > 0 end on it from the other side with M ̸ = N, we get the NS5-type interface between SO(2N + 1) and USp(2M) ′ gauge theories (see figure 6)."
